title: Reservation complete
heading: Reservation complete.
info: Your Prior Notifcation or an update to Prior Notifcation was successfully submitted to your Member State of establishment. Now the Prior Notifcation or its update will undergo a validation performed by your Member State of establishment and by each Member State in which you have requested to beneft from the exemption. If you were not yet assigned by Exempt identifcation number, we will assign one to you and will inform you. You should be notifed about your eligibility to beneft of the exemption within 35 working days. Please note that in specifc cases some Member State(s) may require additional time to complete the validation.
